    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3 in collector-grade condition, featuring the high-revving S54B32 powerplant. This unit has been fastidiously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity; the critical rod bearing service and Besian VANOS overhaul are documented, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural integrity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential, providing the tactile feedback and linear power delivery synonymous with the M division's peak era. The chassis is dialed-in with fresh bushings and OEM dampers, maintaining the original suspension geometry. Zero signs of oxidation or thermal cycling fatigue in the engine bay. This is a turn-key, investment-quality specimen for the enthusiast who prioritizes mechanical perfection and documented provenance.",
